sts/src/org.liquibase/liquibase-core/4.17.0/src/test/java/org_liquibase/liquibase_core/ExecutablePreparedStatementBaseTest.java`\n\nThe new test exercises `ExecutablePreparedStatementBase` through Liquibase’s public prepared-statement execution path using `InsertExecutablePreparedStatement` with a `PostgresDatabase`. It reaches:\n\n- `ExecutablePreparedStatementBase.<clinit>` via class initialization and resource bundle loading\n- `stmt.getClass().getMethod(\"executeWithFlags\", int.class)`\n- `executeWithFlagsMethod.invoke(stmt, 1)`\n\nNo metadata files or unrelated test projects were modified. I did not run tests locally per the workflow instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_041d42507f5b9dce016a2302848058819093e2f3813bd66ff7\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 470, "output": 2191, "cacheRead": 27136, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29797, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780679250224, "responseId": "resp_041d42507f5b9dce016a230252f4b08190902373e45273cc7c"}}
